parameters: We will now begin Saruyama's trial.
Has the defense also completed their preparations?
It is up to the defense attorney to break through this.

First, the prosecutor, please explain the overview of this
case.

Kanade, the victim, was taking a bath in the lake on
top of the hill as a way to relax.
(These people are really engrossed, aren't they...)

Eventually, she heard rustling sounds and went to check,
something ran away with the sound of grass rustling.
I am speaking, but the defense attorney...

(Hmm... I just said it for now, but... I wonder if there's a
hole somewhere...)
Saruyama is not that kind of person!
Are you sure you witnessed Saruyama?
Saruyama has no motive to steal panties!
Saruyama is not that kind of person!
Isn't he/she that kind of person?

Saruyama has a previous record of staring at their smartphone
with a lewd expression, saying Uhyoo~ I've got a super
cute girl! even in their everyday life!
And on top of that, their name is Saru!
Is it possible that Saruyama stole the panties?
Y-Your Honor, I request a witness.
(Now... you were about to say boss, right?)
Ah, ah... It's not Kenta, it's that... I'm Genta.
We have brought in a passerby named Genta as a witness.
I'm Genta, who happened to pass by.
(For now, just go along with it)
Can you explain the situation at that time?

N-No, I mean, I was climbing up the back mountain to go
hunting.
Saruyama has no motive to steal panties!
As you can see, Kanae-chan is cute.

That's why Saruyama has more than enough motive to steal
panties!
\C[6]I was climbing up the back mountain to go hunting.
There is a contradiction in your testimony just now!
Um... Is there none, after all?
Yes, I went to go hunting.
What did you go hunting for?

\C[6]It was a place where rabbits and wild boars were often
seen, so I went hunting.
Objection! There is a contradiction in your testimony just now!
Um... Is there none, after all?
Did you go hunting for wild boars without any equipment?

The defense attorney is just trying to buy time with
irrelevant questions!
Defense attorney, please stop with the nonsense.

\C[6]Um... well... there's a straight path up the back mountain
that leads to the lake.
The path up the mountain leads to the lake?
Please take a look at this map.
This is a map of the cottage at the entrance, right?

Yes. This cottage is built in a valley, so the terrain is
somewhat complex.

However, there is only one path to go up the mountain! It's a
straight path.

In order to cross the mountain, you must climb the stone
steps at the fork in the road before reaching the lake,
rather than passing through the lake!
Does the plaintiff have any objections?
Witness, please stick to stating only the facts.
Actually, I went to pick mushrooms instead...

You might think I'm not useful at all despite being big.
Hehe...
Hikaru-chan, are you unexpectedly good at giving speeches?

(It feels like they self-destructed on their own over
there.)

Anyway, since it turned out like this, there is insufficient
evidence and Saruyama is innocent...
The mistake I made was that I misspoke the location.
His testimony has not been denied.
I request an additional witness here.

Ah, the gateway to victory is not so easily obtained, Lord
Hikaru.
(Since you're a ninja, try doing something)
Are you sure about being single-minded?
Well, honestly, it's not something certain...
This is the only route I know.

\C[6]When we passed that lake, we suddenly heard a scream and
hurriedly ran to see what happened...

There is meaning! There is a contradiction in the testimony
just now!

Um, we left here around 12 o'clock. I think it was
probably around 12:15.
At that time, I saw Saruyama-kun rushing over in a panic.

(No, what's with your reaction... Did you really steal a
glance...)

(Hmm... I wonder if there's any weak point that I can pick
on...)
(Wait, you mean climb towards the lake?)
Press X to question when \C[6]yellow dialogue\C[0] is active.

And on the suspicious \C[6]yellow line\C[0], press the
Shift key and then press the X or Z key
to raise an objection.
I expect great things from you, Lord Hikaru. Nin nin.
Well then, witness, please introduce yourself.
We ended up agreeing without even saying it out loud.

Akane and I both looked down, desperately trying to hold
back our laughter.
Well then, Renka-san. Let's talk about what you saw.
Oh, Prosecutor-sama. I don't like such stiff words.
Please call me Renka-chan~ in a friendly manner.
Hmm, well then, let's say there was no testimony...
Oh my, your embarrassed face is also cute.
...Tsugumi also has a lot of hardships, huh.
Akane is lying face down on the desk, trembling all over.
With a calm and clear mind...
\C[6]Being alone at the cottage is boring.

There is significance! There is a contradiction in the
testimony just now!
Um... Is there none, after all?
What were you doing alone at the cottage?

\C[6]Is there anything I can help with? I was going around
asking people.

There is significance! There is a contradiction in the
testimony just now!
Um... Is there none, after all?

So I thought everyone might be working hard, and went to
look for them.

\C[6]But, at that time! Suddenly, a single monkey passed by with
a whoosh!
Renka... You definitely said monkey, right?
Can you please be a little more clear?
What is this monkey you're talking about...
That must be referring to Saruyama, right?

Big monkeys are cute in their own way, but we're talking
about a small monkey right now.
So... that means it's not Saruyama who's here, right?
It's the first time I've seen a big monkey today.

But there is also evidence that Saruyama was seen at the
scene...!

It has become clear that the one who ran away with the
panties in their mouth was not Saruyama, but a real
monkey!
Well~ It seems like the truth has become clear, huh.

The real culprit who stole Kanae's panties... was a
monkey.
Well then, can't you find those panties?
Ugh~ They were my favorite panties...
When you come back, can you buy one for me, Hikaru?
It's good that it's become clear...

And so, the incident where Kanae had her panties stolen
has come to a close.

Saruyama, who was accused as the culprit, successfully proved
his innocence, and Kanae is planning to steal an
expensive underwear from my wallet.
I don't know why the monkey took the underwear.

Kanae's pink panties with a ribbon... They must be happy
there...
(Every time they react like this, what should I do...)

Please don't react to panties even if you're not in middle
school!
Indeed, they had panties in their mouth, right?

Yes, they were pink panties with a cute ribbon attached! I
definitely saw them!
Are you sure that those panties were stolen?
So now! Please show me your panties!
What are you saying! Are you crazy? Die, you idiot!
Isn't it normal to write about panties?!
Why are you so confident like that!

\C[6]And then, our eyes met... but they quickly panicked and
ran to the opposite side.

There is significance! There is a contradiction in the
testimony just now!
Um...don't you have any, after all.
Our eyes met because we were close by, right?
Yes, we were very close by.

But when I came to my senses, I was already in the middle
of the forest, running away.

(Hmm, what should I do... There seems to be some opening
somewhere...)
